long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Maps Hub Search’s singular focus is preparing you for your journey.

Never get lost again. Never arrive late. And never run out of gas! Join the thousands of delighted Maps Hub Search users. All the top search tools are together in one place—always for free.

Get accurate, easy-to-understand maps and directions with Maps Hub Search. And ensure that all of your web searches take you there with geo-optimized Yahoo default search.

As your trusted travel-planning companion, Maps Hub Search sets your new tab page to Maps Hub Search and your default search engine to Yahoo. Unified and harmonious:

- Get directions from your location to a preferred destination quickly
- Quick links for easy access to commonly used maps and navigation apps
- Optimized searches for locations and much more

Click “Add to Chrome” to install Maps Hub Search.
